      <scopecontent id="aspace_75784649eab68dc9387f09a5e2356020">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographs by C. B. Wells of the Yale residential colleges, various academic buildings, commencement 1936, and scenes of Yale and New Haven in winter during the 1930s. Included are photographs taken after the 1938 hurricane.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
